ta-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612091\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bfc1665702686994.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bfc1665702686994.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bfc1665702686994.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bfc1665702686994\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The \n                                BorderWidth widget property defines the line width (in pixels) of the border that is displayed around the widget if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> property is selected.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__section_w787ab1b5b1_w788ab1b5_w789ab1\"> BorderWidth\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__p_d102488e1_d102489e1_d102490e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"BorderWidth=5\"</code>\n</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12074e1_d12075e1_d12076e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12074e1_d12075e1_d12076e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12074e1_d12075e1_d12076e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12074e1_d12075e1_d12076e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12074e1_d12075e1_d12076e1__entry__2\">Positive integer indicating the border line\n                        width in pixels. The minimum value is 0 and the maximum value is 10. Default\n                        is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__section_pv3_rpt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d642814e107\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__table_d12077e1_d12078e1_d12079e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__section_qlq_spt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d642814e143\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__p_d102497e1_d102498e1_d102499e1\">Changing the width of the border around the grid\n            widget resizes the viewport (the inside dimensions) of the grid. As a consequence, the\n            Viewport_Resized trigger is fired.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__section_mlz_tpt_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d642814e152\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__ul_hhd_vpt_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bfc1665702686994__li_d41477e1_d41478e1_d41479e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"clg1695282025414.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" title=\"The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.\">egrid (Grid)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/buu1719592046867.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger Viewport_Resized</a><p>Interactive trigger that handles processing whenever the Grid widget (excluding row headers, column headers, and scroll bars) is resized.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612091\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612091\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Border Width (BorderWidth) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The BorderWidth widget property defines the line width (in pixels) of the border that is displayed around the widget if the Frame property is selected. BorderWidth = Number Example: \"BorderWidth=5\" Value Description Number Positive integer indicating the border line width in pixels. The minimum value is 0 and the maximum value is 10. Default is 1 . Usage Dynamic? Yes Dependencies: Description Changing the width of the border around the grid widget resizes the viewport (the inside dimensions) of the grid. As a consequence, the Viewport_Resized trigger is fired. Applies To egrid (Grid) Related Links trigger Viewport_Resized Interactive trigger that handles processing whenever the Grid widget (excluding row headers, column headers, and scroll bars) is resized. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}